    "en": {
      "title": "A breakdown of the first machine at Norochchole",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the Minister of Electricity and Energy Mr. Kanchana Wijesekera, the first generator of the Norochchola coal plant has broken down due to a technical fault.",
        "He says that the technical teams are working to identify the technical defect and the second Norochchola machine is currently undergoing essential maintenance.",
        "However, the minister said that the third machine is operational and West Coast and other fuel plants will be operated to manage the fuel demand."
      ],
